**Topic:** Audience building over search dependency

### Summary
In another short video, Kevin reinforces the idea that declining search clicks require marketers to rethink acquisition strategies. He again positions audience building as the long-term solution for maintaining growth in an environment where AI and evolving search experiences reduce website traffic.

